reviewText: Was really excited to get this Dvd set for a x-mass gift. It arrived in an orderly manner.
Need to return. It will not play on my DVD player. I get Region - ERROR.  Not real sure how to but will be sending back this week.
I love this series and it is great to see the episodes in order on the DVD since we don't get them here in America much anymore, and we never got all the episodes.

I love this program.  I rank this program up there with MASH, not because of content, but due to the fact that I can watch these episodes any time they are on.  They are well written and have a great well-defined ensemble cast.  Since this program is only available on my local PBS station, these DVD sets are a great way to view these programs.

I prefer to get these in the British PAL format, and highly recommend anyone purchasing these to check the sellers description closely to determine whether they will work in their DVD player.
First of all, the DVD arrived very fast and as described  One of the best shows ever made, cheers you up just watching it.  I would defintely buy from this person again and highly recommend.
great received it and enjoyed all the shows will be buying more will be buying more in the comming months
